entries.title: Twitter Suspends Over 25 Accounts That Track Billionaires’ Private Planes
entries.description: The suspended accounts include one that followed the private plane of Elon Musk, Twitter’s owner.

entries.title: How to Use Parental Controls on Your Child’s New Phone
entries.description: Apple and Google have upgraded their built-in software for managing the mobile experience, but you have many options for digital supervision.

entries.title: Are Mushrooms the Future of Alternative Leather?
entries.description: MycoWorks uses mycelium, the substance in the root structure of mushrooms, to make Reishi, which has the look and feel of leather. Big-name companies are very interested.

entries.title: Sam Bankman-Fried and FTX Engaged in Fraud for Years, Prosecutors Say
entries.description: A criminal indictment unsealed on Tuesday and a complaint by the S.E.C. describe years of wrongdoing in Sam Bankman-Fried’s crypto empire.
